variables.name: Income
variables.description: Total taxable income for tax calculation.

variables.name: Bracket_1
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 1: 1.40% on the portion of income up to $9,600. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_2
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 2: 3.20% on the portion of income over $9,600 up to $14,400. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_3
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 3: 5.50% on the portion of income over $14,400 up to $19,200. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_4
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 4: 6.40% on the portion of income over $19,200 up to $24,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_5
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 5: 6.80% on the portion of income over $24,000 up to $36,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_6
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 6: 7.20% on the portion of income over $36,000 up to $48,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_7
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 7: 7.60% on the portion of income over $48,000 up to $125,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_8
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 8: 7.90% on the portion of income over $125,000 up to $175,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_9
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 9: 8.25% on the portion of income over $175,000 up to $225,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_10
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 10: 9.00% on the portion of income over $225,000 up to $275,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_11
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 11: 10.00% on the portion of income over $275,000 up to $325,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: Bracket_12
variables.description: Taxes for Bracket 12: 11.00% on the portion of income over $325,000. Always included in the sum; 0 if income does not reach this bracket.

variables.name: FinalTaxes
variables.description: Sum of Bracket_1 through Bracket_12 in numerical order. Includes zeros from brackets that do not apply. Calculation must always add all twelve brackets explicitly.

rules.translation: FinalTaxes is greater or equal to 0
